{"tid":1449513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T15:19:24.000Z","uid":25614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4354d091522151ab408b87a1a6a1c870366bf5","tid":1449513,"uid":25614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a4496820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=7f72856d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"0a35eb766db05581df3377d0a04a59beb421c486","tid":1449513,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"開Post未"},{"pid":"e16122d3851ebb2cf827d91e9795d424177febf0","tid":1449513,"uid":77692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a35eb766db05581df3377d0a04a59beb421c486","tid":1449513,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"開Post未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"<i